nodes.text: Preserve Our Wild Endangered Resources Party

The POWER Party, short for Preserve Our Wild Endangered Resources Party, was a political organization on the planet Telos IV. Created in 44 BBY, it was founded, led, and consisted solely of Thani resident, Andra. It opposed the Telosian government's plan to give the UniFy Corporation control over Telos's National parks and Sacred places, for which the organization was outlawed.
